nars.concept.util

Interface BeliefTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Task>, TaskTable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBeliefTable

    public interface BeliefTable
extends TaskTable
    A model storing, ranking, and projecting beliefs or goals (tasks with TruthValue). It should iterate in top-down order (highest ranking first)
